==English==
===Etymology===
{{wikipedia}}
From JakeBrake<sup>TM</sup> brand compression brakes.  Though a brand name, this term is often used to refer to the device in general.

===Noun===
'''jake [[brake]]'''

#{{slang}} Especially on [[trucks]], an [[engine]] [[compression]] [[brake]] that closes the valves in an engine in order to slow the vehicle; an [[engine]] [[retarder]].

